'You cannot use the "Symfony\Component\HttpClient\Psr18Client" as the "psr/http-factory" package is not installed. Try running "composer require nyholm/psr7".'
'You cannot use the "Symfony\Component\HttpClient\Psr18Client" as the "psr/http-client" package is not installed. Try running "composer require psr/http-client".'
* An adapter to turn a Symfony HttpClientInterface into a PSR-18 ClientInterface.
* Run "composer require psr/http-client" to install the base ClientInterface. Run
* "composer require nyholm/psr7" to install an efficient implementation of response
* and stream factories with flex-provided autowiring aliases.
'You cannot use the "Symfony\Component\HttpClient\Psr18Client" as no PSR-17 factories have been provided. Try running "composer require nyholm/psr7".'
'You cannot use the "Symfony\Component\HttpClient\HttplugClient" as no PSR-17 factories have been found. Try running "composer require nyholm/psr7".'
'You cannot use "%s()" as the "nyholm/psr7" package is not installed. Try running "composer require nyholm/psr7".'
